<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>내 버킷리스트 카드</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gaegu&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* 기본 카드 디자인 (자유롭게 수정 가능) */

        .card {
            width: 300px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, #ffffde 0%, #fff9db, #f4d291 100%);
            padding: 15px 15px 35px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px 20px 5px 60px;
            box-shadow: 3px 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            /* 배지의 기준점이 되기 위한 필수 속성 */
            position: relative;
        }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            transform: rotate(-1deg);
        }

        .card h2 {
            color: #651818;
            font-size: 1.7rem;
            font-family: "Gaegu";
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #651818;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-family: "Gaegu";
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        i {
            color: #9363529d;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-family: "Gaegu";
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        h1,
        span {
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #ffd1d1;
            text-shadow: 2px 1.5px 1px #5d8f40dd;
        }

        /* 1. 배지 (absolute) 관련 CSS를 작성하세요 */
        .badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -5px;
            right: -10px;

            background-color: rgb(227, 55, 55);
            color: white;
            padding: 2px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 5px 3px 2px #ffa4244f inset,
                -5px -3px 2px #b929893f inset,
                2px 2px 2px #64025784;
            transform: rotate(10deg);
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* 2. 비밀 메모 (visibility) 및 hover 효과 관련 CSS를 작성하세요 */
        .secret {
            padding: 30px 30px;
            visibility: hidden;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover .secret {
            visibility: visible;
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .stikerA {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0px;
            right: -25px;
            width: 100px;
            height: 30px;

            background-color: rgba(250, 246, 229, 0.717);
            border-radius: 2px;
            box-shadow: 1px 2px 2px #00000046;
            transform: rotate(-30deg);
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .stikerB {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0px;
            left: -25px;
            width: 100px;
            height: 30px;

            background-color: rgba(239, 234, 212, 0.717);
            border-radius: 2px;
            box-shadow: 1px 2px 2px #00000046;
            transform: rotate(-30deg);
            z-index: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="card">
        <div class="badge">
            <h1><span>🔥중간고사</span><br>D-12</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="stikerA"></div>
        <div class="stikerB"></div>


        <img src="https://cdn.kinnso.ai/laravel/posts/20250114-nomad/content/1736906048_digital_nomad.jpg" alt="바다 풍경">

        <h2>✨ 초윤이의 꿈</h2>
        <p>✈️ 1. 해외 한달살기</p>
        <p>🎮 2. 혼자 게임 만들기</p>

        <i class="secret">일단 시험부터...^^</i>

    </div>
</body>

</html>
